title: Frank Lloyd Wright Gilded Undated Planner
description:
Organize your schedule with both weekly and monthly sections in this undated planner from Galison. Featuring designs from Frank Lloyd Wright, this conveniently sized planner features an embossed cover with gold foil accents, gilded page edges, and an elastic closure.

  • Hard Cover with Foil-Stamp Detail
  • 160 Lined Pages
  • Gilded Page Edges
  • Acid-free paper
  • Elastic Closure
  • Size: 5.25 x 7.25", 130 x 180mm
